fields.name: Carbon Fiber UD Fabric
fields.description: Carbon Fiber UD fabrics is weaved by carbon fiber through 0° and 90°. Regard 0° as the main direction. And then 90° direction. Proceed to biaxial fabrics, according to different requirements, customers can choose different density.

fields.name: Carbon Fiber Roving (Plain Weave)
fields.description: Carbon Fiber Roving (plain) is weaved by carbon fiber through 0° and 90°. According to different requirements, customers can choose different density.

fields.name: Carbon Fiber Roving (Twill Weave)
fields.description: Carbon Fiber Roving (twill) is weaved by carbon fiber through 0° and 90°. According to different requirements, customers can choose different density.

fields.name: Carbon Fiber Multiaxial fabrics
fields.description: Carbon fiber multiaxial fabric is weaved by the carbon fiber yarn arrangement angle 0 degrees /90 degrees / + 45, A carbon fiber with polyester thread and weaving fabric.

fields.name: Carbon Fiber Flat Cloth
fields.description: The carbon fiber precursor is non destructively expanded and then warp and weft knitted. The weaving process has uniform tension, which solves the problems of deviation and deformation in the prepreg process. The fabric surface is smooth and beautiful. The warp and weft yarn of widened carbon fiber fabric has small degree of buckling in the fabric, reduces the bending and "grid" phenomenon of fiber bundle in the fabric, reduces the gap rate, improves the surface flatness of the fabric, and the composite material has high fiber volume content and superior mechanical properties.

fields.name: Carbon Fiber Surfacing Mat
fields.description: Carbon Fiber surface Mat( CST) Products, mainly used in the surface of carbon fiber products, can improve the corrosion resistance of the surface of the products and enhance the compressive strength, anti leakage, prolong service life. The product itself has uniform dispersion of the fiber, soft texture, fiber surface smoothness, low glue content, resin soak speed and film of good characteristics.

fields.name: Carbon Fiber Satin Fabric
fields.description: Carbon fiber satin cloth is a two-way fabric made of carbon fiber yarn with 0 ° and 90 ° flat weaving process. According to different product requirements, carbon fiber satin cloth with different gram weight can be selected.

fields.name: Basalt Fiber UD fabric
fields.description: Basalt Fiber UD fabric is weaved by basalt fiber through 0° and 90°、 Regard 0° as the main direction and then 90° direction to process to a kind of biaxial fabric. According to different requirements, customers can choose different density

fields.name: Basalt Fiber Plain fabric
fields.description: Basalt Fiber Plain fabric, purchasing basalt fiber yarn with high performance by twisting after the whole process of weaving and weaving. Regard 0° as the main direction to process to a kind of biaxial fabric. According to different requirements, it can be woven into a low density of good permeability of light and light fabric, can also be woven into high density and high strength of the fabric.
